    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Sphere 3》是一款拥有丰富世界、细腻剧情与独特场景的MMORPG。玩家将体验多样的成长系统、激烈的联盟战争，以及充满秘密与谜团的广阔世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/397040/extras/72891d59b7661253aa848c56560f8147.poster.avif?t=1764167190\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/397040/extras/72891d59b7661253aa848c56560f8147.webm?t=1764167190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/397040/extras/72891d59b7661253aa848c56560f8147.mp4?t=1764167190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Sphere 3》中，战争永不停歇。数百名玩家参与宏伟的城堡围攻战，使用攻城槌与弩炮；在竞技场中战斗以证明自己的优越；组成氏族与联盟，为了主宰世界而进行大规模战争。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/397040/extras/7d2e1e27d3b9970d144e339f1e4fbec8.poster.avif?t=1764167190\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/397040/extras/7d2e1e27d3b9970d144e339f1e4fbec8.webm?t=1764167190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/397040/extras/7d2e1e27d3b9970d144e339f1e4fbec8.mp4?t=1764167190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了玩家对战，游戏还提供丰富的PvE内容。您可以潜入神秘的地下城，参与对抗巨大世界首领的大规模战斗，消灭成群怪物。击杀它们可获得珍贵战利品——从稀有配方和制作资源，到强大的传奇物品。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/397040/extras/223b7abab293fee15434cca87119d649.poster.avif?t=1764167190\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/397040/extras/223b7abab293fee15434cca87119d649.webm?t=1764167190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/397040/extras/223b7abab293fee15434cca87119d649.mp4?t=1764167190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Sphere 3》以宏大剧情为基础。世界如何诞生？恶魔为何憎恨人类？谁想奴役人类？住在孤塔中的老巫师又与这一切有何关联？您将在超过1000个多样化任务中找到答案，任务将带您穿越被施咒的森林、炎热的沙漠和寒冷的山脉。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/397040/extras/87d77d46d1d9039c42d233ac2bb2a064.poster.avif?t=1764167190\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/397040/extras/87d77d46d1d9039c42d233ac2bb2a064.webm?t=1764167190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/397040/extras/87d77d46d1d9039c42d233ac2bb2a064.mp4?t=1764167190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >便捷的<strong>非锁定战斗系统</strong>为动态战斗增添了色彩，玩家需持续瞄准才能击中敌人。正确的移动和精准的瞄准可以规避伤害，同时对敌人造成沉重打击。这为战术提供了空间，并能展现真正的技术。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>大规模PvP战斗</strong>：在世界各地战斗，占领城堡，组建氏族与联盟，宣战并展现您的优越。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态战斗系统</strong>：借助非锁定战斗系统，玩家可躲避攻击并造成巨大伤害，胜负由技术决定。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为大规模战斗优化</strong>：即使在数百名玩家参与的最大规模战斗中，也能享受稳定的帧率。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>史诗级攻城战</strong>：运用大量攻城器械攻占和防守城堡，战术与技术决定战果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>9种深度成长职业</strong>：根据个人游戏风格创建与众不同的角色。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富PvE内容</strong>：探索危险地下城，消灭特殊敌人，挑战世界首领，还可与其他玩家协作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发达的经济与制作</strong>：成为传奇工匠，您打造的武器、护甲或珠宝将在拍卖行中备受追捧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样化活动</strong>：游戏会举办独特事件，如阻止危险法师、对抗邪教徒、拯救世界免受瘟疫等，成功者可获得独特奖励。 </p></li></ul>",
